12. ALGORITHMS USED
A. SGPA Algorithm
1. totalCredits = sum(credits of all subjects)
2. weightedGP = Œ£(gradePoint √ó credit)
3. SGPA = weightedGP / totalCredits

B. Percentage Algorithm
percentage = (total marks / number of subjects)

C. Grade Conversion
90-100 ‚Üí A+
80-89  ‚Üí A
70-79  ‚Üí B+
60-69  ‚Üí B
50-59  ‚Üí C
40-49  ‚Üí D
<40    ‚Üí F

